## Supabase Tables — Schema Reference

### signals
```sql
id              UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
received_at     TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
asset           TEXT NOT NULL           -- e.g. BTC/USDT
direction       TEXT NOT NULL           -- long | short | close
timeframe       TEXT                    -- e.g. 1h, 4h, 1d
signal_type     TEXT                    -- e.g. MACD crossover
raw_payload     JSONB                   -- full TradingView webhook JSON
```

### deliberations
```sql
id                      UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
signal_id               UUID REFERENCES signals(id)
started_at              TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
bull_score              INT
bull_thesis             TEXT
bear_score              INT
bear_thesis             TEXT
bull_rebuttal           TEXT
bear_rebuttal           TEXT
quant_ev                NUMERIC
quant_data              JSONB
macro_regime            TEXT            -- risk-on | risk-off | neutral
macro_flag              BOOLEAN
sentiment_score         INT
sentiment_summary       TEXT
news_interrupt          BOOLEAN DEFAULT false
risk_approved           BOOLEAN
position_size_pct       NUMERIC
final_decision          TEXT            -- trade | hold | veto
orchestrator_reasoning  TEXT
outcome                 TEXT            -- filled after trade closes
pnl_pct                 NUMERIC         -- filled after trade closes
```

### trades
```sql
id                  UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
deliberation_id     UUID REFERENCES deliberations(id)
entry_price         NUMERIC
entry_time          TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
exit_price          NUMERIC
exit_time           TIMESTAMPTZ
position_size_usd   NUMERIC
pnl_usd             NUMERIC
pnl_pct             NUMERIC
mode                TEXT DEFAULT 'paper'    -- paper | live
exchange            TEXT
```

### agent_reputation
```sql
id                      UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
agent_name              TEXT            -- bull | bear | quant | macro | sentiment
week_ending             DATE
dissent_correct_rate    NUMERIC
overall_accuracy        NUMERIC
current_weight          NUMERIC DEFAULT 1.0
trades_sampled          INT
```

